### About the Project
Jaguar Emulator is a v18 Habbo Emulator written in C#. The goals of the emulator are to make a simple, lightweight, and multi-platform Habbo Hotel emulator targeting the **Version 18 Habbo Client**. 

### Authors and Contributors
@zgillis - Lead Developer
